{"tid":2217256,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：警察暴力掟蘋果落街（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-25T09:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T10:32:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec98b930939b579728a47f65f1bb43a743937106","tid":2217256,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/3D4A4B7DO5AX7PPPVYQNEFA45A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2F3D4A4B7DO5AX7PPPVYQNEFA45A%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=7c28b23e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2F3D4A4B7DO5AX7PPPVYQNEFA45A%2F&h=befa1e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/3D4A4B7DO5AX7PPPVYQNEFA45A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：警察暴力掟蘋果落街（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uckRtenW5YSVEWbtXAUP22dEmA4=/1183x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4HBT4XWI5G4TPNLYGJDTWLESM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuckRtenW5YSVEWbtXAUP22dEmA4%3D%2F1183x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4HBT4XWI5G4TPNLYGJDTWLESM.jpg&h=bc3afe4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警察喺fb貼出meme圖，慘被掉落街嘅蘋果仔同《蘋果》logo好相似。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察喺社交媒體動作多多，最近就喺facebook專頁出咗張meme圖，本來好地地教人慎防電話騙案，但就懶幽默咁將「蘋果」掟落街。無獨有偶，粒蘋果造型同《蘋果日報》logo非常相似，似乎影射緊要將《蘋果》掟落街！<br />\n<br />\n講返呢張meme圖，。。。。。。。。，警察鼓吹暴力行為，又算唔算煽動仇恨呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民：難怪咁多死因無可疑<br />\n<br />\n呢個小學雞式文宣網民唔多受落，大批網民留言恥笑警方借文宣終於肯承認想殺蘋果，同埋最叻掉人落街，亦有網民讚差人「誠實」：「難得誠實一次喎！搞唔掂就掟人落街」，「香港警察做事真的光明磊落！毫不掩飾直接說把人從高處掉下！男子漢！難怪這一年多那麼多人被警察扔下來死亡警察也說沒可疑」。身為紀律部隊，居然喺網上鼓吹暴力，成日話「與暴力割席」嘅特區政府今次唔知點睇警察教壞細路喇。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"576a1e6dec8639a2098d17e150842859e2aae6ca","tid":2217256,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"係咪暗示成日做呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}